<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">| <strong class="text-white font-semibold">ROLL</strong> | <strong class="text-white font-semibold">LIFT</strong>                                                        | <strong class="text-white font-semibold">SMASH</strong>                       | <strong class="text-white font-semibold">GRAPPLE</strong>                |
| :------: | --------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------- | -------------------------- |
