|    <strong class="text-white font-semibold">25</strong>    | Ride a wild horse through dangerous terrain.     | Evade notice with minimal cover in ample light.    | Open a door secured by a sequence of elaborate locks. |
|    <strong class="text-white font-semibold">30</strong>    | Ride an enraged beast through dangerous terrain. | Evade notice with no cover in full daylight.       | Disable an incredibly sensitive and deadly trap.      |</p>
