<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">| <strong class="text-white font-semibold">ROLL</strong> | <strong class="text-white font-semibold">PERCEIVE</strong>                                              | <strong class="text-white font-semibold">SENSE</strong>                                                           | <strong class="text-white font-semibold">NAVIGATE</strong>                                             |
