|    <strong class="text-white font-semibold">15</strong>    | Win the trust of a cautious stranger or talk your way into a noble’s party. | Earn room and board in a low-end tavern or impress a large crowd. | Trick an average merchant.     |
|    <strong class="text-white font-semibold">20</strong>    | Win the trust of a sympathetic foe or talk your way into an enemy’s party.  | Earn lodging in a high-end tavern or impress a full theater.      | Trick a trained courtier.      |
|    <strong class="text-white font-semibold">25</strong>    | Turn an enemy against their ruler or talk your way into a fae court.        | Earn your keep in a royal court or impress a full colosseum.      | Trick a spymaster.             |
|    <strong class="text-white font-semibold">30</strong>    | Talk a hostile god into granting you a boon.                                | Save yourself from execution after offending the queen.           | Trick a god.                   |</p>
